{"tid":2243146,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解羅生門會係用嚟形容事件撲朔迷離","createTime":"2020-10-14T13:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T16:57:58.000Z","uid":151389,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"825c64b52bcc614b7622caf54b5a534178ded107","tid":2243146,"uid":151389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:39:50.000Z","msg":"明明羅生門電影嘅內容明明係竹林中嘅故事<br />\n羅生門本身係講一個有原則嘅武士因為走頭無路　放棄原則搶阿婆衫，講人性黑暗<br />\n<br />\n點解當時套電影要改名羅生門而唔係叫返做竹林中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到啲冇睇過小說嘅人以為羅生門先係講唔同人講埋晒啲矛盾野嘅嗰個故事，當埋係用嚟形容撲朔迷離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4526ddb95be9896192317340b51f64ef3a353d","tid":2243146,"uid":88663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:43:33.000Z","msg":"你搭咗自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6617d065865d60c50e5807d03cd401a74f84ba","tid":2243146,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"呢單野都係羅生門黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b6f170b091d870da661df982ccc4bec5de2aea","tid":2243146,"uid":43493,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:48:47.000Z","msg":"成件事本身就係一個羅生門嚟<br />\n原本係叫竹林中<br />\n之後又有人話係羅生門，結果就搞咗個羅生門出嚟"},{"pid":"3e4b2dc46f756f153e391d102100a89414fb116d","tid":2243146,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T14:07:02.000Z","msg":"我鐘意呀，吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8380782bdc6c858902ba27325a2f34a7e5b63036","tid":2243146,"uid":366281,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T14:08:03.000Z","msg":"羅生門多數係指發生一件事，當事人各自嘅講法有所矛盾，唔知邊個講真邊個講假，旁觀者就眾說紛紜，好難下定論"},{"pid":"8f4452c4080b4576da3756cf9b306c0baa5154b6","tid":2243146,"uid":134226,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T14:09:19.000Z","msg":"芥川嘅竹林中同羅生門